        "subject": "LU-19161 kfilnd: kfilnd_nl_set doesn't understand timeout",
        "message": "LU-19161 kfilnd: kfilnd_nl_set doesn't understand timeout\n\nLNET_NET_KFILND_TUNABLES_ATTR_TIMEOUT added to\nkfilnd_ni_lnd_tunables_attr by https://review.whamcloud.com/57514.\nkfilnd_nl_set() was not updated to handle the new attribute, so add it\nnow.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: c3d1ca4478 (\"LU-18566 lnet: dynamically configure timeouts\")\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I38757b53e3ae55f153661dda6d5f76f980681054\n"
